攻克新冠病毒离不开科研，最新进展有哪些。
To conquer the new crown virus is inseparable from scientific research, recent developments.
2020-02-15 19:07:29来源： 财新网作者：周东旭责任编辑：张帆。
2020-02-15 19: 07: 29 Source: Caixin Network Author: Zhou Dongxu Responsibility Editor: Zhang Fan.
2020年02月15日 19:07。
15 February 2020 at 19: 07.
来源于。
From sources.
财新网。
Caixin Net.
可以听文章啦！。
Listen to the passage.
临床救治方案的优化和药物筛选、检测技术和产品、病毒病原学和流行病学、疫苗研发、动物模型构建是当前新冠肺炎科技攻关的五个主攻方向，取得了阶段性进展。
Optimization of clinical treatment and drug screening, detection techniques and products, viral etiology and epidemiology, vaccine development, animal model construction are the five main directions of the current scientific and technological attack of new crown pneumonia, and have made progress in stages.
临床救治方案的优化和药物筛选、检测技术和产品、病毒病原学和流行病学、疫苗研发、动物模型构建是当前新冠肺炎科技攻关的五个主攻方向。
Optimization of clinical treatment and drug screening, detection techniques and products, viral etiology and epidemiology, vaccine development, animal model construction are the five main directions of the current technological solutions to the new crown pneumonia.
。
.
相关报道【财新周刊】封面报道|保卫湖北【财新周刊】封面报道|四大ICU主任详解病毒 来自最前线的防治之策【财新周刊】封面报道|37位记者四万字全景调查：新冠病毒何以至此？解药|前两批瑞德西韦辗转运抵武汉，新冠临床试验争分夺秒解药|新冠病人血浆疗法非神药 难以大规模应用患者粪便中分离出新冠病毒 病毒粪便传播未有定论解药|无临床试验结果，院士李兰娟两款新冠荐药数据遭质疑专家：新冠病毒存在血液传播的可能。
Rhett Butler and Rhett Rhett Rhetoric Ready to Spread New Crown Virus in Wuhan The first two batches of Rhetoric virus faeces have arrived in Wuhan The first two batches of Rhetoric virus faeces have arrived in Wuhan.
【财新网】（记者 周东旭）临床救治方案的优化和药物筛选、检测技术和产品、病毒病原学和流行病学、疫苗研发、动物模型构建是当前新冠肺炎科技攻关的五个主攻方向。
Optimization of clinical treatment and drug screening, detection techniques and products, viral etiology and epidemiology, vaccine development and animal model construction are the five main directions of the current scientific and technological treatment of new crown pneumonia.
2月15日，国务院联防联控机制举行发布会，介绍了科研最新进展。
On February 15, the Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council held a press conference to update scientific research.
。
.
科技部社会发展科技司司长吴远彬介绍，在五大主攻方向方面取得了阶段性进展。
Ministry of Science and Technology Secretary for Social Development and Science Wu Yun-bin introduced, in the five major directions of progress in stages.
病毒病原和流行病学方面，初步排除新冠肺炎的来源与已知家禽家畜的关系，提出蝙蝠是最有可能携带新冠病毒的源头。
In terms of virulence and epidemiology, the association between the origin of new crown pneumonia and known domestic animals was preliminarily excluded, suggesting that bats were the most likely source of the new crown virus.
。
.
在动物模型方面，成功构建新冠肺炎感染的小鼠、猴子等动物模型，为开展药物和疫苗的安全性、有效性评价提供基础条件。
In animal models, animal models such as mice and monkeys were successfully constructed to provide basic conditions for safety and efficacy evaluation of drugs and vaccines.
。
.
在检测诊断方面，在已有七个诊断检测试剂获批上市的基础上，正在加快推进现场快速检测产品的研发和应用。
On the basis of the approval of seven diagnostic testing reagents on the market, the research and development and application of the rapid detection products on the spot are being accelerated.
。
.
在药物研发和临床救治方面，有些药品筛选和治疗方案取得积极进展，正在推进临床试验，部分临床救治建议已经纳入诊疗方案。
With regard to drug research and development and clinical treatment, some drug screening and treatment programmes have made positive progress, clinical trials are progressing and some clinical treatment recommendations have been incorporated into clinical protocols.
。
.
在疫苗研发方面，并行开展了灭活疫苗、核酸疫苗、重组疫苗等多条技术路线的研发。
In the field of vaccine development, research and development of inactivated vaccines, nucleic acid vaccines and recombinant vaccines have been carried out in parallel.
。
.
吴远彬还提到，为高效有序地推进全国应急科技攻关，专门印发《关于加强新冠肺炎科技攻关相关管理的通知》，引导科技人员弘扬科学家精神、勇挑重担，把论文写在疫情第一线，把研究成果运用到战胜疫情之中。
Wu also mentioned that in order to efficiently and orderly advance the national emergency science and technology, the notice on strengthening the management of scientific and technological problems related to the New Crown Pneumonia was issued to guide scientific and technological personnel to carry forward the spirit of scientists and shoulder the heavy burden, put the paper on the front line of the epidemic and apply the research results to the fight against the epidemic.
。
.
药物：部分药物初步显示良好临床疗效。
Drugs: Some drugs initially showed good clinical efficacy.
研发有效的临床救治药物，努力提高治愈率，降低病死率，是当前应急攻关的重中之重。
It is the most important task to develop effective clinical medicine, improve cure rate and reduce fatality rate.
科技部生物中心主任张新民介绍，全国的科研团队利用计算机模拟筛选、体外酶活性测试等方法对7万多个药品或化合物进行筛选，遴选出5000个可能有效的候选药物，在普通冠状病毒感染的细胞水平上进行初筛，之后选定了100个左右的药物在体内开展新型冠状病毒的活性实验。
Zhang Xinmin, director of the Biological Center at the Ministry of Science and Technology, said research teams across the country screened more than 70,000 drugs or compounds using computer simulations, in vitro enzyme activity tests, selected 5,000 potentially effective candidate drugs, screened them at the level of common coronavirus-infected cells, and selected about 100 drugs to carry out new coronavirus activities in vivo.
。
.
经过多轮筛选，科研攻关组聚焦到少数几个药品。
After several rounds of screening, the research team focused on a few drugs.
张新民说，磷酸氯喹、伦地西韦、法匹拉韦等一批药物，先后开展临床试验，目前部分药物已经初步显示出良好的临床疗效。
Zhang Xinmin said that chloroquine phosphate, Lundisevir, Fabiravee and other drugs have been carried out in clinical trials, and some drugs have initially shown good clinical efficacy.
。
.
比如，磷酸氯喹，目前正在北京、广东等十多家医院开展临床研究，累计入组患者超过100例。
chloroquine phosphate, for example, is currently undergoing clinical research in more than a dozen hospitals in Beijing and Guangdong, with more than 100 patients in the group.
湖南省也将启动磷酸氯喹的多中心临床试验。
A multicenter clinical trial of chloroquine phosphate will also be launched in Hunan Province.
临床结果初步显示，磷酸氯喹对新冠肺炎有一定的诊疗效果。
The clinical results showed that chloroquine phosphate was effective in the diagnosis and treatment of new crown pneumonia.
。
.
又如，法匹拉韦，目前在深圳开展临床试验，入组患者达到70余例，包括对照组，初步显示较明显的疗效和较低的不良反应。
Fapiravi, for example, is currently undergoing clinical trials in Shenzhen, with more than 70 patients in the group, including the control group, showing initially significant efficacy and low adverse reactions.
治疗后第3到4天，用药组的病毒核酸转阴率显著高于对照组。
After treatment for 3-4 days, the rate of nucleic acid conversion was significantly higher in the drug group than in the control group.
。
.
再比如，瑞德西韦，是一种国外公司研制的用于抗埃博拉病毒感染的药物，目前在国外的临床试验还没有全部做完。
Rhetsevius, for example, a foreign company developed to fight Ebola virus infection, has not completed clinical trials abroad.
中国科学家开展了体外实验显示，具有对新冠病毒较好的抑制作用和安全性。
Chinese scientists have carried out in vitro experiments showed that the new crown virus has a good inhibition and safety.
该药在美国也实现了对一位患者的成功治疗。
The drug also achieved a successful treatment for one patient in the United States.
目前，在武汉推动在十余家医疗机构开展临床研究，已入组重症患者168例，轻型、普通型患者17例。
At present, Wuhan has promoted clinical research in more than a dozen medical institutions, and has enrolled 168 severe patients and 17 light and ordinary patients.
。
.
疫苗：并行安排多条技术路线，部分疫苗进入动物试验阶段。
Vaccines: Several technical routes are arranged in parallel, and some vaccines enter the animal testing stage.
由于新冠病毒是一个新病原体，疫苗研发难度比较大、周期比较长。
Because the new crown virus is a new pathogen, it is more difficult to develop vaccine and the cycle is longer.
张新民介绍，为确保尽早研发成功，在科研攻关应急项目中并行安排了多条技术路线，包括灭活疫苗、mRNA疫苗、重组蛋白疫苗、病毒载体疫苗、DNA疫苗等并行推进。
To ensure the early success of R & D, a number of parallel technological routes have been put in place, including inactivated vaccines, mRNA vaccines, recombinant protein vaccines, viral vector vaccines and DNA vaccines.
。
.
当前部分疫苗品种已经进入动物试验阶段。
At present, some vaccine varieties have already entered the animal experimental stage.
张新民说，目前来看，我们国家各研究团队的研发进度与国际进展基本保持同步。
'So far, the research teams in our country have kept pace with international developments, 'Mr. Zhang said.
。
.
中科院微生物研究所研究员严景华介绍，科学院团队承担的工作是重组的蛋白疫苗。
Yan Jinghua, a researcher at the Institute of Microbiology at the Chinese Academy of Sciences, said the team was working on a recombinant protein vaccine.
重组蛋白疫苗是把一个病原体最有效的抗原成份基因拿出来，进行体外重组，表达蛋白，然后制成疫苗。
A recombinant protein vaccine is a gene that takes out the most effective antigen component of a pathogen, recombinates it in vitro, expresses the protein, and then makes the vaccine.
这种疫苗不需要场所，比如病毒特征的灭活苗需要一个相应生物安全等级的场所。
The vaccine does not require a site, such as a biosecurity site for inactivated virus signatures.
。
.
严景华说，“目前疫苗进展非常顺利，团队这两年做MERS疫苗，在疫苗设计过程中取得了一些好的结果。
"The vaccine is progressing very well and the team has had some good results in vaccine design over the past two years," he said.
新冠病毒出现以后，很快把这个策略和方法用在新冠病毒疫苗的设计，目前已经设计完成了这个疫苗，已经在动物体内进行测试，看看免疫效果，还要进行安全性评价。
With the advent of the new canopy virus, this strategy and approach was quickly applied to the design of the new canopy virus vaccine, which has been designed and tested in animals to see the effects of immunization and safety evaluation.
现在正在做的工作还有生产工艺研发的过程。
Work is also under way to develop production processes.
”。
"
严景华还介绍，过去是串联的方式，一个试验结束看看结果后再进行第二个试验，现在是把周期变成并联方式，很多试验同步推进，争取疫苗早日上市。
Yan also introduced that the past is a series of ways, after a trial to see the results of a second test, now is to turn the cycle into parallel, many trials synchronous advance, for the vaccine early market.
。
.
动物试验：针对冠状病毒的动物模型最有效可能是灵长类。
Animal testing: The most effective animal model for coronavirus is probably a primate.
动物试验是药物进行临床前非常重要的一个环节。
Animal testing is one of the most important aspects of drugs before clinical trials.
中国科学院副秘书长、中国科学院院士周琪介绍，目前为止针对冠状病毒的动物模型最有效的依然可能是灵长类动物，比如猕猴。
Zhou Qi, deputy secretary-general of the Chinese Academy of Sciences and a member of the Chinese Academy of Sciences, said primates, such as macaques, could still be the most effective animal models for coronavirus.
所以，在前期动物模型的造模和动物评价上，在灵长类动物里已经看到和人相似的症状，包括病毒的载量的变化，包括肺部的CT影像的检验，这批模型已经通过验证，即将投入到药物的筛选和功能评价上。
So, in the modeling and animal evaluation of preanimal models, similar human-like symptoms have been seen in primates, including changes in viral load, including CT images of the lungs, which have been validated and are about to be invested in screening and functional evaluation of drugs.
同时也在其他类型动物的开发上不断发力。
At the same time in the development of other types of animals continue to exert efforts.
。
.
药物研发的难点在哪里？周琪介绍，应对冠状病毒引起的肺炎，大家都期待一个新药的出现，但新药的出现有客观限制，有时间要求，也有关键流程和步骤。
What are the difficulties in drug R & D? Zhou Qi said that in response to the coronavirus-induced pneumonia, we all look forward to the emergence of a new drug, but there are objective limitations, time requirements, and key processes and steps.
比如，一定要在动物模型做很多长期的评价以后才有可能走到临床。
For example, it is important to do a lot of long-term evaluation of animal models before it becomes clinically possible.
任何一个环节对科学家而言都是一个非常艰难的过程，同样也是一个必然要经历的过程。
Any link is a very difficult process for scientists, but also an inevitable process to go through.
国家已经开启了绿色通道，各种各样的行政环节全部向治疗救治病人开放，但科学的事情含糊不得，科学不能降低标准，一定还要按照科学的药物研发流程做完。
The state has opened a green channel, and all kinds of administrative links are open to patients for treatment. However, scientific matters are not allowed to be ambiguous, science cannot lower standards and must be completed in accordance with scientific drug research and development procedures.
。
.
张新民也说，疫苗作为一种应用于健康人的特殊产品，对其安全性的要求是第一位的，疫苗研发必须遵循科学规律以及严格的管理规范，需要给科研人员一定的时间来开发出安全、有效的疫苗产品。
Zhang also said the vaccine as a special product for healthy people, its safety requirements are the first, vaccine development must follow the scientific law and strict management norms, need to give researchers time to develop safe, effective vaccine products.
。
.
病毒溯源：正组织科研团队论证穿山甲是否为中间宿主。
Virus traceability: Research teams are being organized to demonstrate whether pangolin is an intermediate host.
病毒溯源对揭示病毒来源及其进化规律，对于消除疫情源头，防止疫情扩散都非常重要。
Virus traceability is very important for revealing the source of virus and its evolution, eliminating the source of epidemic and preventing the spread of epidemic.
科技部社会发展科技司司长吴远彬介绍，中国疾病预防控制中心病毒所检测了585份华南海鲜市场及武汉多家生鲜市场环境标本及动物标本，其中33份新冠病毒阳性，其中31份来自经营野生动物的西区，通过这样集中的数据提示此次疫情可能与野生动物交易有关。
The Centre for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) virus has detected 585 samples of the seafood market in South China and several samples of animals in Wuhan. Thirty-one of them were found to be New Crown Virus-positive, including 31 from the western part of the country where wild animals operate.
。
.
吴远彬还说，中国动物卫生与流行病学中心的团队检测了4800余份近年来收集的猪、禽、犬、猫等动物样品，均为阴性，通过这样的结果可以初步排除新型冠状病毒来源于家禽家畜。
Wu said the team from the China Animal Health and Epidemiology Center tested more than 4,800 animal samples collected in recent years, including pigs, poultry, dogs and cats.
之前，中国科学院武汉病毒所通过对新冠病毒基因组序列的比对，也显示出蝙蝠最有可能是新冠病毒的天然宿主。
Previous comparisons of the genome sequence of the new crown virus by the Wuhan virus of the Chinese Academy of Sciences have also shown that bats are the most likely natural hosts of the new crown virus.
。
.
对于华南农业大学团队的研究，提出穿山甲可能是新冠病毒的中间宿主之一。
For the team at South China Agricultural University, it is suggested that pangolin may be one of the intermediate hosts of the new crown virus.
对此，吴远彬介绍，正组织有关科研团队进行论证，对新冠病毒从穿山甲到人的传播，也在进一步加紧相关研究。
To this, Wu Yubin introduced, is organizing the research team to carry on the argumentation, regarding the new crown virus from the pangolin to the human transmission, also is stepping up the related research.
。
.
重患治疗：开展干细胞技术临床应用。
Severe Acute Respiratory Therapy: Clinical Application of Stem Cell Technology.
张新民介绍，科研攻关组组织了针对重症治疗的新技术和新产品研究，从目前来看部分产品和技术取得了良好的临床效果。
Zhang Xinmin said the research team has organized research on new technologies and new products for severe treatment, and that some products and technologies have achieved good clinical results.
一是采集治愈患者恢复期血浆，用于重症患者治疗。
One is to collect and cure patients convalescent plasma for the treatment of severe patients.
处于恢复期患者的血浆中存在大量的保护性抗体，可以用于对重症患者的治疗。
There are a lot of protective antibodies in the plasma of convalescent patients, which can be used for the treatment of severe patients.
截至目前，在武汉市江夏区第一人民医院、武汉金银潭医院等多家医院共对11位重症患者进行了治疗，治疗后临床症状明显改善，各项检测指标全面向好，没有明显的不良反应。
So far, 11 patients with severe diseases have been treated in the First People's Hospital of Jiangxia District of Wuhan and the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital in Wuhan.
。
.
第二个方面是开展干细胞技术在重症救治方面的临床研究。
The second aspect is to develop the clinical research of stem cell technology in severe treatment.
经过严格的临床前安全性、有效性评价，以及严格的质量检定，干细胞产品在遵照当前干细胞临床应用规范和药品临床试验规定的前提下对若干重症患者进行了治疗，也初步显示安全有效。
After rigorous pre-clinical safety, efficacy evaluation, and rigorous quality verification, stem cell products have been used to treat a number of patients with severe diseases in accordance with the current norms for clinical application of stem cells and the provisions of clinical trials of drugs, and have also initially shown to be safe and effective.
。
.
确保尽快恢复正常医疗秩序。
Ensure a speedy return to normal medical order.
在新闻发布会上，国家卫生健康委新闻发言人、宣传司副司长米锋还特别提示各地卫生健康部门要加大工作指导力度，确保医疗机构尽快恢复正常的医疗秩序。
At the press conference, the press spokesman of the National Health Council, deputy director of the publicity department Mifeng also urged local health departments to strengthen work guidance to ensure that medical institutions as soon as possible to restore normal medical order.
。
.
米锋还通报，来自世界卫生组织及有关方面的专家将于本周末陆续抵京。
Mifeng also informed that experts from the World Health Organization and related areas will arrive in Beijing later this week.
此前，中方相关部门同世界卫生组织先遣组总干事高级顾问布鲁斯•艾尔沃德深入交流，共同商定了中国—世界卫生组织新型冠状病毒肺炎联合专家考察组的重点领域和活动日程。
Prior to the meeting, Chinese authorities had in-depth exchanges with Bruce Alvold, Senior Advisor to the Director-General of the WHO Advance Team, and jointly agreed on the key areas and schedule of activities of the China-WHO Joint Expert Team on Coronavirus Pneumonia.
联合专家考察组将与联防联控机制相关部门进行深入交流，之后将对三个省市进行考察。
The joint expert mission will have in-depth exchanges with the relevant departments of the Joint Defence Mechanism, followed by visits to the three provinces and municipalities.
。
.
